<p>You may opt out of receiving promotional or marketing communications from us by following the instructions in our communications or by emailing us at <a href="mailto:info@emailagency.com">info@emailagency.com</a>&nbsp;Even if you opt out of marketing messages, you may still receive transactional messages related to your interactions with us. To opt out of having your information shared with third parties for their marketing purposes, you may contact us, and if you wish to stop receiving communications from those third parties, you must contact them directly.</p>
<p>For choices related to interest-based advertising, please refer to the “Digital Advertising &amp; Analytics” section below.</p>
